WEBVTT

00:09.444 --> 00:14.231
There is great danger in me.

00:14.275 --> 00:17.713
For those who do not understand
these mysteries

00:17.756 --> 00:23.197
shall fall into a
torment called Because,

00:23.240 --> 00:26.374
and there be ripped
apart by the teeth

00:26.417 --> 00:29.377
of Reason.

00:29.420 --> 00:33.685
The answers do
not exist without,

00:33.729 --> 00:35.731
but within.

00:37.515 --> 00:39.952
You can't see past
your own obsessions.

00:39.996 --> 00:42.520
Having aa vision
of going to the moon

00:42.564 --> 00:44.348
doesn't make it
any less impossible.

00:44.392 --> 00:48.178
Why is it you think that Mesulam
and Braxton sent me to D.C.?

00:48.222 --> 00:50.137
They needed someone
they could trust

00:50.180 --> 00:52.139
to make a sensible presentation.

00:52.182 --> 00:55.055
An actual scientist and not
someone who believes they can

00:55.098 --> 00:57.622
will things into existence.

00:57.666 --> 01:00.756
Before we make
our offering to the Great Beast,

01:00.799 --> 01:03.193
concentrate

01:03.237 --> 01:06.327
on the answers you seek.

01:06.370 --> 01:07.937
Parsons.

01:07.980 --> 01:11.419
These parts are corroded, sir.

01:11.462 --> 01:13.421
Paying me overtime's
gonna be a lot cheaper

01:13.464 --> 01:14.987
than replacing the machine.

01:15.031 --> 01:17.120
I didn't come down here
to reprimand you.

01:17.164 --> 01:20.471
I've noticed a change
in you. You're punctual.

01:20.515 --> 01:23.996
No more lastminute absences,
even working overtime.

01:24.040 --> 01:25.148
Even when no one asked you to.

01:25.172 --> 01:27.783
Yeah. I can only assume

01:27.826 --> 01:29.717
this has something to do
with your little side project

01:29.741 --> 01:32.004
not panning out. Its aims
are no longer worthy

01:32.048 --> 01:34.050
of my abilities, sir.

01:34.094 --> 01:37.662
Well, Caltech's loss
may be Pueblo Powder's gain.

01:37.706 --> 01:41.927
How would you feel about
being made supervisor?

01:41.971 --> 01:43.799
For I am in pain,

01:43.842 --> 01:46.671
desperate for the
release of union.

01:54.636 --> 01:56.159
May you be granted
the accomplishment

01:56.203 --> 01:57.900
of your true will.

01:57.943 --> 01:59.684
May you be granted
the accomplishment

01:59.728 --> 02:01.295
of your true will.

02:01.338 --> 02:02.644
May you be granted

02:02.687 --> 02:04.385
the accomplishment
of your true will.

02:06.256 --> 02:10.042
So what do you think
about the offer?

02:10.086 --> 02:12.132
Certainly a big step up.

02:12.175 --> 02:15.352
Would mean more money.

02:15.396 --> 02:18.964
More responsibility,
but we could buy a bigger house.

02:19.008 --> 02:20.966
Is that what youwant?

02:21.010 --> 02:23.055
I'm trying to do
the right thing here.

02:23.099 --> 02:25.539
I think you should do whatever
your true will tells you to do.

02:27.277 --> 02:29.453
You can stop that.
I know what you're doing.

02:29.497 --> 02:31.542
What am I doing?

02:31.586 --> 02:34.415
Giving me a taste
of my own medicine.

02:37.026 --> 02:39.289
Why are you so insistent
we go tonight?

02:39.333 --> 02:41.944
Because I'm trying, Jack.

02:41.987 --> 02:43.902
What if I'm not in the mood
to go to a mass?

02:43.946 --> 02:45.295
Well, I want to go.

02:45.339 --> 02:47.950
Would you prefer I go alone?

02:52.824 --> 02:54.739
May you be granted
the accomplishment

02:54.783 --> 02:56.828
of your true will.

02:56.872 --> 02:58.787
May you be granted
the accomplishment

02:58.830 --> 03:00.005
of your true will.

03:00.049 --> 03:01.311
May you be granted

03:01.355 --> 03:03.444
the accomplishment
of your true will.

03:06.490 --> 03:07.796
There you are.

03:07.839 --> 03:09.232
Have you got a second?

03:09.276 --> 03:10.668
Make it quick, frater.

03:10.712 --> 03:12.312
Got to get these done
before mass begins.

03:13.584 --> 03:17.109
I am this close to
my next ascension.

03:17.153 --> 03:20.069
Well, you're not the only one
up for a promotion.

03:20.112 --> 03:21.810
First degree?

03:21.853 --> 03:23.681
Man and brother of the faith? No.

03:25.727 --> 03:28.251
To supervisor.

03:28.295 --> 03:30.384
At Pueblo Powder.

03:30.427 --> 03:34.562
Supervisor.

03:34.605 --> 03:36.999
I don't know whether
I should accept.

03:38.957 --> 03:40.959
Guess you'll know what
to focus on at mass.

03:41.003 --> 03:42.526
The right answer
will reveal itself.

03:42.570 --> 03:44.006
Whether they will

03:44.049 --> 03:48.271
absorption into the infinite,
or to be united

03:48.315 --> 03:50.186
with your chosen and preferred,

03:50.230 --> 03:53.058
I say unto them,
"Love is the law."

03:56.932 --> 03:58.455
May you be granted
the accomplishment

03:58.499 --> 04:02.285
of your true will.

04:02.329 --> 04:04.026
May you be granted
the accomplishment

04:04.069 --> 04:06.985
of your true will.

04:08.987 --> 04:10.119
May you be granted

04:10.162 --> 04:12.817
the accomplishment
of your true will.

04:12.861 --> 04:15.646
Do what thou wilt

04:15.690 --> 04:17.300
shall be the whole of the law.

04:17.344 --> 04:20.260
Love is the law. Love under will.

04:20.303 --> 04:24.568
Come down, O, God,
and become one with Man.

04:24.612 --> 04:29.225
Come down, O, Man,
and become one with Beast.

